Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.73,0:30:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果各位不介意  我坐幾分鐘就走\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll just sit with you a moment. Then I'll be off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.40,0:30:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真的不喝點什么嗎  -不客氣  謝謝你\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}-Are you quite sure? -Quite sure, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.19,0:30:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-葛雷哥近來如何  -他很好\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}-Well, how's Gregor? -He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.66,0:30:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在波羅的海從事海底實驗\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He's been doing underwater research in the Baltic...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.20,0:30:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以最近我們很少碰面\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...so I'm afraid we don't see very much of each other these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.50,0:30:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-如果見到他  記著代我問好  -當然\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}-When you see him, give him my regards. -Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.33,0:30:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們大伙要去那里  上還是下\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Well, where are you all off to? Up or down?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.50,0:30:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正準備回家\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.75,0:30:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛花了三個月的時間  校正柴林科號上的新天線\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We've just spent 3 months calibrating the new antenna at Tchalinko.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.88,0:30:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你呢  -我正要去克萊威斯\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}-What about you? -I'm on my way to Clavius.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.80,0:30:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  是嗎\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Oh, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.87,0:30:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克萊威斯\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Clavius.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.77,0:30:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  請不要介意我太好奇\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Dr. Floyd, I hope you don't think I'm being too inquisitive...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.27,0:30:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也許你可以澄清一下  \N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...but perhaps you can clear up the big mystery 
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.17,0:30:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底那里發生了什么事\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}about what is going on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.19,0:31:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恐怕不太了解你的意思\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm afraid I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.57,0:31:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去兩個星期  克萊威斯發生怪事\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}For the past two weeks...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.49,0:31:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去兩個星期  克萊威斯發生怪事\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...some extremely odd things have been happening at Clavius.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.16,0:31:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真的嗎  -真的\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}-Oh, really? -Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.54,0:31:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如  當你打電話到該基地時  \N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}For one thing, when you phone the base, 
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.40,0:31:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能聽到電話錄音\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}all you get is a recording...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.04,0:31:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重覆的告訴你線路故障\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...which repeats that the phone lines are temporarily out of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.75,0:31:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是他們的裝備故障\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Probably having some trouble with their equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.72,0:31:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  起先我們也是這么想  \N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's what we thought at first, 
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.45,0:31:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到現在為止已經十天了\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but it's been going on now for 10 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.89,0:31:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說在過去十天中  你們無法與任何人聯絡\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You haven't been able to contact anyone for 10 days?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.85,0:31:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.52,0:31:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.73,0:31:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一件事  兩天前我們有一輛火箭巴士\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}There's another thing. Two days ago, one of our rocket buses...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.61,0:31:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拒絕在克萊威斯緊急迫降\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...was denied permission for an emergency landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.74,0:31:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就真的有些奇怪了\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That does sound odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.94,0:31:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  恐怕這件事將會引起爭執\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm afraid there's going to be a bit of a row about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.41,0:31:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕迫降是違反  國際航空暨太空協定\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Denying the men permission to land violates the IAS Convention.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.49,0:31:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  那當然  機員們都平安歸來了嗎\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yes, of course. Did the crew get back all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.54,0:31:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是的  很慶幸  \N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Fortunately, they did. 
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.40,0:31:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  很高興聽到這樣\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Well, I'm glad about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.59,0:32:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛博士對你不愿討論的問題  \N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}At the risk of pressing you on 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.72,0:32:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一再追問  也許有些冒犯\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}a point you seem reticent to discuss...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.80,0:32:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我可不可以  直接的問你一個問題\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...may I ask you a straightforward question?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.59,0:32:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Well, certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.81,0:32:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦白說  我們有可靠的情報指出\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Frankly, we have had some very reliable intelligence reports that...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.39,0:32:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在克萊威斯發生一種  不明來源  十分嚴重的傳染病\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...quite a serious epidemic has broken out at Clavius.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.02,0:32:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在克萊威斯發生一種  不明來源  十分嚴重的傳染病\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Something, apparently, of an unknown origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.28,0:32:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該就是事情的真相吧\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Is this, in fact, what has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.91,0:32:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉  史麥斯博士\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, Dr. Smyslov, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.37,0:32:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法與你討論這件事\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...I'm really not at liberty to discuss this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.71,0:32:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點我了解\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.34,0:32:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個傳染病可能  很容易就傳染到我們的基地\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But this epidemic could easily spread to our base.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.76,0:32:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須要知道事情的真相\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We should be given all the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.05,0:32:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.89,0:32:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我已說過  我無法討論這個問題\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}As I said, I'm not at liberty to discuss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.73,0:33:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定不改變主意來一杯嗎\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Won't you change your mind about that drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.73,0:33:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定  現在我真的必須走了\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}No, I'm positive. I really must be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.32,0:33:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你和你太太能一起參加  六月舉行的國際航空會議\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I hope you and your wife come to the IAC Conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.57,0:33:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會想辦法  希望屆時能前來參加\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I hope we can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.11,0:33:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如你們能來  記得寶貝女兒一起帶來\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}If you do, bring that darling little daughter with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.37,0:33:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要看學校假期而定\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That'll depend on school vacations and all that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.54,0:33:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以  一定帶來\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}If we can, we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.79,0:33:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記不論何時  到美國來一定要來找我\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You've got an invitation if you ever get to the States.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.92,0:33:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  葛雷哥和我  都期待著去看你們\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Gregor and I will look forward to seeing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.63,0:33:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  艾琳娜  再見\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Goodbye, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.09,0:33:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很榮幸見到你們  史麥斯洛夫博士\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's been a pleasure meeting you all. Dr. Smyslov.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.18,0:33:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛博士  不管你是什么理由  \N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Whatever the reasons for your visit, 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.46,0:33:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去克萊威斯  祝你幸運\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}the very best of luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.35,0:33:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.64,0:33:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位女士\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.64,0:33:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(俄語)
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.35,0:36:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}零重力廁所  乘客使用前應先閱讀說明
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.32,0:41:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  赫伍森博士  我拍完了\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Excuse me, Dr. Halvorsen. I'm through now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.74,0:41:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-謝謝各位  -不客氣\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}-Thank you very much, gentlemen. -You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.55,0:41:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  大家和我一樣都非常高興\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.22,0:41:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  大家和我一樣都非常高興\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...I know you will all want to join with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.26,0:41:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎我們杰出的朋友和同事\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...in welcoming our distinguished friend and colleague...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.35,0:42:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自國家太空航行委員會  赫伍德  佛洛伊德博士\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...from the National Council of Astronautics, Dr. Heywood Floyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.81,0:42:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛博士今天特別來到  克萊威斯參加我們的工作\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Dr. Floyd has come up specially to Clavius to be with us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.24,0:42:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在簡報前  我想他一定很樂意說幾句話\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Before the briefing, he'd like to have a few words with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.78,0:42:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛博士\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Dr. Floyd?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.80,0:42:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝赫伍森博士\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Thank you, Dr. Halvorsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.01,0:42:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  很高興回來和大家在一起\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Hi, everybody. Nice to be back with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.14,0:42:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先我帶來豪爾博士的口信\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}First, I bring a personal message from Dr. Howell...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.98,0:42:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對各位所作的犧牲  表示由衷的感激\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...who has asked me to convey his deep appreciation...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.02,0:42:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對各位所作的犧牲  表示由衷的感激\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...for the many sacrifices you've had to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.36,0:42:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時他對各位在科學史上  \N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And, of course, 
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.27,0:42:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最有意義的發現  表示祝賀\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}his congratulations on your discovery...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.74,0:42:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時他對各位在科學史上  \N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...which may prove to be among the most significant 
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.05,0:42:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最有意義的發現  表示祝賀\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}in the history of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.62,0:42:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在.  .\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Now...
