Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.10,1:00:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全像睡著般沒有知覺  \N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's exactly like being asleep. You have no sense of time.
