Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.15,1:01:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赫爾  在這次任務中  你有一大堆的責任\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Hal, you have an enormous responsibility on this mission...
