Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.40,1:02:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否因此會產生挫折感\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...by your dependence on people to carry out actions?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.74,1:02:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不會  \N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Not in the slightest bit.
