Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.25,1:02:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的任務范圍  \N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My mission responsibilities 
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.16,1:02:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括整個太空船的作業\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}range over the entire operation of the ship...
