Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.69,1:02:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺如何\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...in such close proximity with Hal?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.52,1:02:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我和他非常的接近\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's like what you said earlier.
