Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.11,1:02:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于他會說話  \N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You quickly get adjusted to the idea that he talks, 
