Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.88,1:03:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信赫爾真有感情嗎\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Do you believe that Hal has genuine emotions?
