Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.99,1:04:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅  富蘭克  親愛的  祝你生日快樂\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Happy birthday, darling!
