Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.98,1:04:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎  上星期我們還上電視呢\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We were on TV last week.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.65,1:04:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你母親和我  還有大衛父母都接受訪問\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Your mom and I and Dave's parents were asked...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.52,1:04:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我們對于杰出兒子的感受\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...what we thought of our illustrious son.
