Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.49,1:05:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興買禮物送你  但請告訴我可以花多少錢\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll be glad to get the gift, but tell me how much to spend.
