Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.54,1:05:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我幫你處理好了  \N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...I think I straightened it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.33,1:05:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我和會計室的人談過\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I talked to the accounting office yesterday...
