Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.51,1:05:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不出還有什么要說\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I can't think of anything else to say.
