Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.69,1:05:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你生日快樂\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Happy birthday to you.
