Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.40,1:05:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝親愛的富蘭克生日快樂\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Happy birthday, dear Frank
