Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.42,1:06:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好像你對\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Looks like you're right. I resign.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.84,1:06:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  這盤棋下得很愉快\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Thank you for a very enjoyable game.
