Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.73,1:07:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大衛  你畫得很不錯\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's a very nice rendering, Dave.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.03,1:07:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為你有很大進步\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I think you've improved a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.66,1:07:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-請你再拿近一點好嗎  -當然可以\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}-Can you hold it a bit closer? -Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.83,1:07:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是亨利博士嗎  是的\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's Dr. Hunter, isn't it?
