Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.38,1:08:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問你一個私人問題  不介意吧\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...do you mind if I ask you a personal question?
