Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.80,1:08:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我的好奇  但在過去的幾星期中\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Well, forgive me for being so inquisitive...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.35,1:08:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懷疑你們對這次任務  是否另有想法\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...but lately I've wondered...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.68,1:08:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懷疑你們對這次任務  是否另有想法\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...whether you might be having second thoughts about the mission?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.77,1:08:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什么意思\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.69,1:08:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很難解釋  \N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Well, it's rather difficult to define.
