Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.87,1:08:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的疑心從未完全解除\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...that there are some extremely odd things about this mission.
