Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.23,1:09:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信大家在出發前都聽過  在我們四周流傳的一些謠言\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...strange stories floating around before we left.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.23,1:09:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關于月球上  有某樣東西被挖掘出來的謠言\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Rumors about something being dug up on the moon.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.94,1:09:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從不相信這些謠言\N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I never gave these stories much credence...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.45,1:09:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就某些已發生的事來說  \N{\fn方正大黑简体}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}...but particularly in view of some other things that have happened...
